parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Blower Motor Failure and Electrical System Issues
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the blower motor and electrical system can cause the air conditioning and heating system to malfunction, leading to a loss of defrosting and defogging capabilities, which can impair visibility and increase the risk of accidents.
symptoms: The blower motor fails to operate
the air conditioning and heating system malfunctions
burning smells and smoke emanate from the vents
the defroster and defogger do not work
and the wires and wiring harness melt.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Recall Repair Issues and Parts Distribution Disconnect
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The delayed or incomplete recall repairs can lead to continued safety risks, such as fires, and inconvenience to vehicle owners.
symptoms: Vehicle owners experience delays or unavailability of parts for recall repairs
incomplete repairs
and continued safety issues despite recall notifications.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Fire Hazards and Electrical System Failures
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The electrical system failures can cause fires, which can lead to serious injuries or fatalities.
symptoms: Fires occur in the vehicle
often due to electrical system failures
burning smells and smoke emanate from the vents
and the wires and wiring harness melt.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of other safety-critical systems can increase the risk of accidents and injuries.
symptoms: The car horn fails to work
and the vehicle suddenly loses acceleration
posing a safety risk to the occupants and other drivers.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the transmission can cause the vehicle to lose power, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The vehicle suddenly loses power
the transmission slips out of gear
the vehicle jerks or shakes
the "wrench" light illuminates on the dashboard
the vehicle is unable to shift into gear.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the transmission cooling line can cause the transmission to fail, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The transmission cooling line ruptures
causing the transmission to fail
the vehicle loses power
the "wrench" light illuminates on the dashboard.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the electronic throttle body can cause the vehicle to stall or lose power, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The vehicle stalls or loses power
the "wrench" light illuminates on the dashboard
the vehicle is unable to accelerate.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the parking gear can cause the vehicle to roll away, leading to accidents or property damage.
symptoms: The vehicle rolls away while parked
the gear shifter assembly is faulty.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The excessive electrical drain can cause the vehicle's battery to drain, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The vehicle's battery drains excessively
the gear shifter assembly module is faulty.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the electronic throttle body can cause sudden deceleration, loss of power, and engine shutdown while driving, which can lead to accidents, especially when merging or turning in front of approaching vehicles.
symptoms: The vehicle suddenly loses power
the "wrench" warning light appears on the dashboard
the engine goes into limp mode
the vehicle can only idle or move at a slow speed
the vehicle shuts down while driving
and the check engine light may come on.
